Class JawrWicketLinkResolver

java.lang.Object
  net.jawr.web.wicket.JawrWicketLinkResolver
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, org.apache.wicket.IClusterable, org.apache.wicket.markup.resolver.IComponentResolver
public class JawrWicketLinkResolver
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.apache.wicket.markup.resolver.IComponentResolver

This class defines a tag resolver which handles <wicket:jawr> tags. The tasks of this resolver will be to : - add a "transparent" WebMarkupContainer to transparently handling child components. - create the right component depending on the tag defined inside <wicket:jawr>
